      "description": "Local Rate Limit 차단/허용 추이 (Envoy Lua 로그)\n\n**Local RL = ingressgateway Pod별 token bucket** (Pod 간 카운터 공유 X. Pod N개면 실효 limit ×N)\n\n**기본 (전체 경로)**: 100 req/s, burst 100\n**IP별 (perClient)**: 50 req/s, burst 100\n**경로별 (perRoute)**:\n- /auth/ : 10 req/s, burst 20\n- /payment/ : 5 req/s, burst 10\n- /signup : 3 req/s, burst 5\n\n**제외 경로**: /load-test/, /health, /healthz, /ready, /metrics, /actuator/health\n**응답**: 429 + Retry-After:60\n**로깅**: 차단된 요청만 (onlyLimited:true)\n\n*설정: ca-staging/values/istio/values-istio-security.yaml > rateLimiting.local*",
